# Day 02 — Services & Tags

##  Ansible — Install & Enable Nginx

---
- name: Install nginx
  hosts: all
  become: yes
 
  tasks:
    - name: Install nginx
      yum:
        name: nginx
        state: present
    - name: Enable nginx
      service:
        name: nginx
        state: started
        enabled: yes

